Document: Path2D
Path: godot/classes/class_path2d.rst
Summary: Manages a 2D path with PathFollow2D nodes moving along a Curve2D.

Can have PathFollow2D child nodes moving along a Curve2D. See PathFollow2D for more information on usage. Note: The path is considered as relative to the moved nodes (children of PathFollow2D). As such, the curve should usually start with a zero vector ( (0, 0) ).
