Document: Path2D
Path: godot/classes/class_path2d.rst
Summary: The 'curve' property and its setter/getter methods for defining a 2D path.

Curve2D curve
Method: set_curve(value: Curve2D)
Method: get_curve() → Curve2D
A Curve2D describing the path. The curve property defines the shape of the path, with the setter method allowing assignment of a new Curve2D instance and the getter method retrieving the current curve.